reviewText: Fun video, arrived on time, for a single guy in his thirties, it was all I expected it to be.
Disc plays great & I am very happy with the product and the time I received it!

If you are a fan of the Girls Gone Wild series, you would do well to avoid this one. It doesn't live up to the previous series in terms of quality. Better to buy an R-rated movie you like rather than expect entertainment from this particular edition.
